-01-07T09:51:58.000Z","msg":"唔好為屌而屌 大把外國人都會唔理文法<br />\n理性d得唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"夠大把外國人唔會上連登，咁你又上？"},{"pid":"d46c69fb6514b48f3c56161499c7f928bd08f1ef","tid":522102,"uid":125171,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>enjoy係verb??? 應該係I'm really enjoy&hellip;&hellip;先啱<br />\n利申英文拎2</blockquote>I really <strong><ins>enjoyed</ins></strong></blockquote>原來要用past tense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都以為係而家都好享受所以用present tense<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加ed係因為形容人"},{"pid":"a984522e67573d62310efbb9769395c880d26b4c","tid":522102,"uid":31007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:09:49.000Z","msg":"I hate Kwan Gor as he is &quot;faked toxic penis&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBy Physicist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06d1504f803cbd27ea9c6f18fe22a2b616ffc85","tid":522102,"uid":66203,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"其實呢個都好小事姐<br />\ncommon error來<br />\n好似人地問你頭先dinner好唔好味咁 好多人都會答 I like it 而唔係 i liked it"},{"pid":"4f6f44704376a015b25dd830db1d9d9457d1881b","tid":522102,"uid":10146,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"Enjoy 係 transitive verb 後面要跟object<br />\nEg I really enjoyed myself/my time last night!<br />\n或者直頭講 I had a blast last night<br />\n而家唔係笑佢文法，係佢將中文直譯做英文<br />\n如果係咁, 咁點解唔直接打中文?<br />\nPS Enjoy 都可以係intransitive verb, eg Enjoy!"},{"pid":"cffc6ab49b28c9c69d6005ae9b2f4c977bc1898f","tid":522102,"uid":10146,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"b06d1504f803cbd27ea